      <item>
        <title>Welcome to idblockchain</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Trio is a simple, content-focused, responsive, mobile-friendly &lt;a href=&quot;http://jekyllrb.com/&quot;&gt;Jekyll&lt;/a&gt; theme. Trio comes with support for these things out-of-the-box:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/feed.xml&quot;&gt;RSS feed&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/404.html&quot;&gt;404 page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Markdown syntax highlighting, fenced code blocks, tables, GitHub gists, blockquotes&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Post sharing buttons&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Paginated list of posts&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/2015/09/06/setting-up-disqus-integration/&quot;&gt;Disqus integration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Formspree &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/contact/&quot;&gt;contact form&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Nine color themes&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Support for logos using &lt;a href=&quot;http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome&quot;&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/a&gt; icons&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Full-text search&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;where-is-it&quot;&gt;Where is it?&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Trio lives in a &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ankur-gupta/trio&quot;&gt;GitHub repository&lt;/a&gt;. It is free and open-source with &lt;a href=&quot;http://opensource.org/licenses/MIT&quot;&gt;MIT License&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please feel free to download it, request a feature or report a bug.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
